{"tid":346642,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[PolyU] 招募研究對象！20分鐘！現金$50!","createTime":"2017-08-04T06:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T02:45:12.000Z","uid":133432,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28031e6745ce16dd450c6fa48e7969e5df25cb9d","tid":346642,"uid":133432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:27:58.000Z","msg":"理工大學碩士學生招募研究對象！ <br />\n實驗需時20-25分鐘，需要面對面進行，完成後可即時獲得現金$50! <br />\n<br />\n實驗內容： <br />\n參加者需要利用電腦對一些詞語的真實性作出判斷，整個實驗需時 20-25分鐘，完成後可獲得$50現金報酬。 <br />\n<br />\n參加者要求： <br />\n- 18-35歲人士 <br />\n- 以廣東話為母語 <br />\n- 英文公開試考獲 <br />\n*HKCEE D級或以上; 或 <br />\n*HKDSE 3級或以上; 或 <br />\n*IELTS 總分6分或以上<br />\n<br />\n有意參加，請聯絡Rachel (91068742, rachel.shih@connect.polyu.hk)或 Kate (92019950, kate.wingki.ng@connect.polyu.hk)。<br />\n<br />\n（實驗地點大多為理工大學，有需要時可配合研究對象對較方便的公眾地方如公共圖書館進行）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/142739_9416394f22d15ec2b76daf279ed7eb70.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F142739_9416394f22d15ec2b76daf279ed7eb70.jpeg&h=c21167ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbfd3d44816fbd8e9c94839ad81fc80f3360bc37","tid":346642,"uid":611,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"車錢都蝕鳩埋畀你"},{"pid":"1131133f1436835a873a4809aec6c8cf845296d5","tid":346642,"uid":113509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"50蚊 邊個會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1464987d4df6a53bfdf0b8a445fffe6c09c62d","tid":346642,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"中間食左幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a105cf3f91c7b50364e08748aff91cd1db76de93","tid":346642,"uid":64374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0155a418140e7ac38761c7421b